00:35:54,600 --> 00:35:55,880
Kaew!

256
00:36:11,120 --> 00:36:12,880
Kaew! Kaew…

257
00:36:15,040 --> 00:36:19,400
Please tell me you also feel the same.

258
00:36:20,040 --> 00:36:25,040
When you return from the trip, I’ll tell you.

259
00:36:26,360 --> 00:36:30,880
I’m back. Please wake up and welcome me with your kiss.

260
00:36:34,760 --> 00:36:35,560
Kaew…

261
00:36:38,360 --> 00:36:43,640
You’ve promised me, haven’t you? I’m back now.

262
00:36:44,600 --> 00:36:50,640
Wake up, my dear. Wake up and talk to me.

263
00:36:52,160 --> 00:36:53,520
[For eternity]

264
00:37:03,640 --> 00:37:06,880
I’m back now, my love. My dear Kaewta.

265
00:37:06,880 --> 00:37:09,680
My dear…I’m back.

266
00:37:10,600 --> 00:37:13,280
Please wake up and talk to me, Kaew.

267
00:37:13,280 --> 00:37:15,200
Please…

268
00:37:15,200 --> 00:37:15,920
Kaew!

269
00:37:17,280 --> 00:37:18,640
I’m back.

270
00:37:20,280 --> 00:37:21,920
I’m back now, Kaew.

271
00:37:25,280 --> 00:37:29,800
Son, please try to restrain yourself.

272
00:37:29,800 --> 00:37:32,080
Kaewta is already dead.

273
00:37:34,960 --> 00:37:35,920
Kaew!

274
00:37:46,600 --> 00:37:48,760
Who did this, Father?

275
00:37:50,680 --> 00:37:52,760
Who killed my Kaewta!

276
00:38:02,000 --> 00:38:04,000
Miss!

277
00:38:04,000 --> 00:38:05,160
Miss!

278
00:38:06,440 --> 00:38:10,520
Let’s go now! His Lordship has found out about everything.

279
00:38:10,520 --> 00:38:13,560
He said he would send you to the police,

280
00:38:13,560 --> 00:38:15,800
and even let you take the criminal punishment.

281
00:38:17,640 --> 00:38:19,040
Miss!!!

282
00:38:20,480 --> 00:38:22,040
Miss!

283
00:38:23,320 --> 00:38:27,600
If you’re not coming, I’ll go alone then.

284
00:38:29,040 --> 00:38:31,040
Go on, Som.

285
00:38:46,880 --> 00:38:48,320
Miss!

286
00:39:00,280 --> 00:39:07,160
Sophee…did you kill Kaewta?

287
00:39:11,560 --> 00:39:12,760
Khun Yai!

288
00:39:13,320 --> 00:39:17,520
I’m asking you! Did you kill Kaewta?

289
00:39:19,280 --> 00:39:23,960
Yes, I killed him. He deserved to die.

290
00:39:26,000 --> 00:39:28,560
He seduced you and fooled you to love him instead of me.

291
00:39:28,680 --> 00:39:29,520
Sophee!

292
00:39:33,920 --> 00:39:36,760
Are you going to kill me now, Brother?

293
00:39:37,560 --> 00:39:43,880
Yai, please stop. I’m begging you.

294
00:39:57,480 --> 00:40:03,280
This woman is no longer my sister.

295
00:40:06,360 --> 00:40:12,000
From now on, whether in this life or any other life…

296
00:40:13,040 --> 00:40:15,640
we shall never meet ever again!

297
00:40:20,800 --> 00:40:21,480
Brother!

298
00:40:21,480 --> 00:40:22,440
Khun Yai!

299
00:40:23,080 --> 00:40:24,000
Sophee!

300
00:40:28,000 --> 00:40:28,960
That’s enough!

301
00:40:30,800 --> 00:40:32,800
I can’t believe you’re my daughter.

302
00:40:35,280 --> 00:40:37,760
How can you be so cruel and heartless?

303
00:40:37,920 --> 00:40:39,600
Father…

304
00:40:41,280 --> 00:40:45,440
You shall get…the punishment you deserve.

305
00:40:52,760 --> 00:40:54,480
Miss.

306
00:40:55,680 --> 00:40:58,000
Oh, my dear Miss!

307
00:41:35,640 --> 00:41:43,480
I hereby vow, should the next life exist,

308
00:41:43,480 --> 00:41:48,880
I shall remember this love and pain…

309
00:41:55,520 --> 00:41:58,400
to get back at all of them!

310
00:42:47,880 --> 00:42:53,000
Khun Yai, you haven’t eaten for many days now.

311
00:42:54,120 --> 00:42:58,880
Not even a sip of water. Please, sir.

312
00:42:59,280 --> 00:43:01,480
If you keep going on like this,

313
00:43:07,480 --> 00:43:08,680
Yes, sir.

314
00:43:37,160 --> 00:43:41,560
Khun Yai. I’m going in, sir.

315
00:44:01,000 --> 00:44:02,320
Khun Yai…

316
00:44:28,000 --> 00:44:31,680
Then, I shall follow you, sir.

317
00:44:46,840 --> 00:44:49,160
Kaew. Wake up, Kaew!

318
00:44:49,160 --> 00:44:50,280
You have to run!

319
00:44:50,600 --> 00:44:52,480
Kaew! Kaew!

320
00:45:15,200 --> 00:45:17,080
Oh, you’re awake?

321
00:45:18,800 --> 00:45:22,280
Miss Sophee, what are you doing?

322
00:45:23,480 --> 00:45:27,240
I’m going to make you and the white house disappear from this world.

323
00:45:27,360 --> 00:45:30,200
So that Brother would finally be mine in this life!

324
00:45:33,840 --> 00:45:36,240
Surely, you don’t mean me…

325
00:45:38,080 --> 00:45:43,000
You lied. You said you drew his portrait without having met him before.

326
00:45:44,560 --> 00:45:51,920
But I saw you seducing my man the other day. Just like what you did in the past life.

327
00:45:54,280 --> 00:45:56,440
That wasn’t Khun Yai!

328
00:45:56,800 --> 00:45:58,360
Liar!

329
00:45:59,960 --> 00:46:02,360
Please stop, Miss Sophee.

330
00:46:03,120 --> 00:46:06,120
You have already committed so many sins…

331
00:46:06,840 --> 00:46:09,840
both in this life and the past life.

332
00:46:10,800 --> 00:46:14,720
Please stop now, and I will forgive you.

333
00:46:19,600 --> 00:46:21,000
Never!

334
00:46:21,840 --> 00:46:26,640
As long as you’re still alive, he will never look at me.

335
00:46:38,560 --> 00:46:40,120
Kaew!

336
00:46:41,240 --> 00:46:42,800
No! No!

337
00:46:43,320 --> 00:46:44,720
Don’t!

338
00:46:45,080 --> 00:46:46,360
Please don’t, Miss Sophee! Don’t!

339
00:46:46,360 --> 00:46:48,080
No!

340
00:46:55,080 --> 00:46:56,320
Kaew!

341
00:46:57,840 --> 00:47:00,120
Stop! What are you doing?

342
00:47:00,120 --> 00:47:01,320
What the heck are you doing?

343
00:47:02,320 --> 00:47:03,840
Brother!

344
00:47:04,160 --> 00:47:07,160
Ajarn! He’s not Khun Yai!

345
00:47:08,080 --> 00:47:11,960
You mean that man who looks like me?

346
00:47:15,080 --> 00:47:21,080
Brother! My love! You’re mine…

347
00:47:21,080 --> 00:47:22,640
not his!

348
00:47:22,640 --> 00:47:26,600
Please don’t do this. Let go!

349
00:47:28,120 --> 00:47:30,440
Kaew, I’ve got you.

350
00:47:38,360 --> 00:47:39,720
Watch out!

351
00:47:40,080 --> 00:47:41,720
Ajarn!

352
00:47:56,680 --> 00:47:59,680
No…No! No!

353
00:48:01,640 --> 00:48:04,040
No! No!

354
00:48:44,520 --> 00:48:48,840
Kaew, I’m here. Kaew…

355
00:49:03,520 --> 00:49:05,680
Khun Yai!

356
00:49:17,880 --> 00:49:19,760
Sophee!

357
00:49:35,640 --> 00:49:38,640
