375
00:51:54,760 --> 00:51:56,360
Khun Phra Nai.

376
00:52:07,680 --> 00:52:09,320
Are you leaving, Saen?

377
00:52:09,960 --> 00:52:11,520
It’s such a pity…

378
00:52:11,520 --> 00:52:13,280
