456
01:03:32,280 --> 01:03:35,200
Fine, if you say so.

457
01:03:42,400 --> 01:03:43,360
How are you, Wut?

458
01:03:45,320 --> 01:03:47,200
You’re taking good care of it as always, Saen.

459
01:03:50,200 --> 01:03:51,200
