461
01:03:55,400 --> 01:03:58,280
If you do that again, I’m going to change my name then.

462
01:04:01,360 --> 01:04:03,280
I’m just kidding.

463
01:04:04,240 --> 01:04:06,320
I just want to let you know that I’ll be on a video call for work.

464
01:04:06,440 --> 01:04:08,280
Feel free to take a look around.

465
01:04:09,240 --> 01:04:09,320
